    <item>
      <title>林恩·格兰特 (Linn Grant) 惊艳夺得欧洲巡回赛冠军</title>
      <link>https://apnews.com/article/linn-grant-scandinavian-mixed-soderberg-european-tour-43feaf75b7aec61a25ce6e4d54a73a67</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典选手林恩·格兰特目前已获得两项欧洲巡回赛冠军。她在两年内第二次赢得斯堪的纳维亚混合赛冠军令人震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://apnews.com/article/linn-grant-scandinavian-mixed-soderberg-european-tour-43feaf75b7aec61a25ce6e4d54a73a67</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:28:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小型飞机坠毁 飞行员丧生 亚利桑那州关闭皮卡乔峰州立公园</title>
      <link>https://apnews.com/article/pilot-killed-small-plane-picacho-peak-tucson-8add18cb0ac31de64a475996ec336090</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当局称，亚利桑那州南部的皮卡乔峰州立公园因一架小型飞机在山顶附近坠毁并导致飞行员死亡，公园将关闭直至另行通知。]]></description>
      <guid>https://apnews.com/article/pilot-killed-small-plane-picacho-peak-tucson-8add18cb0ac31de64a475996ec336090</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:13:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
